      "originalText": "join_room(user, room)\nleave_room(user, room)\nkick_user(admin, target)\nmute_user(admin, target)\nunmute_user(admin, target)\npromote_admin(admin, target)\n\nAdmin succession:\nfirst-in -> next user\nbecomes admin on leave",
